public interface PublicCloneable extends Cloneable
An interface that exposes the clone() method. In order to support the cloning of JFreeChart instances, it is advisable to implement this interface for custom plots, renderers and other chart components. If this interface is not implemented, cloning will still be attempted via reflection.
